{"id":281336,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/02/【图说天朝】武汉10秒内两人跳江/","date":"2013-02-28T02:12:12Z","modified":"2013-02-28T02:12:12Z","title":"【图说天朝】武汉10秒内两人跳江","content":"<p>2月27日12时，武汉，记者在长江大桥武昌桥头堡处拍雾霾天气照片，突然有人呼喊“江面上有个人”。在距武昌江滩约百余米处，有一人在水中挣扎，与此同时，又有人爬上大桥护栏，一跃而下，记者来不及阻拦。但不到10秒，两人已被江水吞没。</p>\n\n\t\t<style type='text/css'>\n\t\t\t#gallery-1 {\n\t\t\t\tmargin: auto;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t#gallery-1 .gallery-item {\n\t\t\t\tfloat: left;\n\t\t\t\tmargin-top: 10px;\n\t\t\t\ttext-align: center;\n\t\t\t\twidth: 25%;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t#gallery-1 img {\n\t\t\t\tborder: 2px solid #cfcfcf;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t#gallery-1 .gallery-caption {\n\t\t\t\tmargin-left: 0;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t/* see gallery_shortcode() in wp-includes/media.php */\n\t\t</style>\n\t\t<div id='gallery-1' class='gallery galleryid-281336 gallery-columns-4 gallery-size-thumbnail'><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/02/%e3%80%90%e5%9b%be%e8%af%b4%e5%a4%a9%e6%9c%9d%e3%80%91%e6%ad%a6%e6%b1%8910%e7%a7%92%e5%86%85%e4%b8%a4%e4%ba%ba%e8%b7%b3%e6%b1%9f/8ops8q1300ap0001/'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/02/8OPS8Q1300AP0001-150x150.jpg\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" aria-describedby=\"gallery-1-281337\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/02/8OPS8Q1300AP0001-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/02/8OPS8Q1300AP0001-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</dt>\n\t\t\t\t<dd class='wp-caption-text gallery-caption' id='gallery-1-281337'>\n\t\t\t\t2月27日中午，武汉长江大桥武昌桥头堡，记者在此拍摄雾霾天气照片时，意外拍下轻生者跳桥。\n\t\t\t\t</dd></dl><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/02/%e3%80%90%e5%9b%be%e8%af%b4%e5%a4%a9%e6%9c%9d%e3%80%91%e6%ad%a6%e6%b1%8910%e7%a7%92%e5%86%85%e4%b8%a4%e4%ba%ba%e8%b7%b3%e6%b1%9f/8ops8qne00ap0001/'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/02/8OPS8QNE00AP0001-150x150.jpg\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" aria-describedby=\"gallery-1-281338\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/02/8OPS8QNE00AP0001-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/02/8OPS8QNE00AP0001-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</dt>\n\t\t\t\t<dd class='wp-caption-text gallery-caption' id='gallery-1-281338'>\n\t\t\t\t2月27日中午，武汉长江大桥武昌桥头堡，记者在此拍摄雾霾天气照片时，意外拍下轻生者跳桥。\n\t\t\t\t</dd></dl><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/02/%e3%80%90%e5%9b%be%e8%af%b4%e5%a4%a9%e6%9c%9d%e3%80%91%e6%ad%a6%e6%b1%8910%e7%a7%92%e5%86%85%e4%b8%a4%e4%ba%ba%e8%b7%b3%e6%b1%9f/8ops8ru600ap0001/'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/02/8OPS8RU600AP0001-150x150.jpg\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" aria-describedby=\"gallery-1-281339\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/02/8OPS8RU600AP0001-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/02/8OPS8RU600AP0001-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</dt>\n\t\t\t\t<dd class='wp-caption-text gallery-caption' id='gallery-1-281339'>\n\t\t\t\t当日中午，记者在武汉长江大桥武昌桥头堡处拍摄雾霾照片，突然有人呼喊“江面上有个人”。记者朝大桥下方看去，发现在距武昌江滩约百余米处，有一人在水中挣扎，时隐时现。就在这时，又有人爬上大桥护栏，一跃而下，记者根本来不及阻拦。\n\t\t\t\t</dd></dl><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/02/%e3%80%90%e5%9b%be%e8%af%b4%e5%a4%a9%e6%9c%9d%e3%80%91%e6%ad%a6%e6%b1%8910%e7%a7%92%e5%86%85%e4%b8%a4%e4%ba%ba%e8%b7%b3%e6%b1%9f/8ops8t6700ap0001/'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/02/8OPS8T6700AP0001-150x150.jpg\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" aria-describedby=\"gallery-1-281340\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/02/8OPS8T6700AP0001-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/02/8OPS8T6700AP0001-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</dt>\n\t\t\t\t<dd class='wp-caption-text gallery-caption' id='gallery-1-281340'>\n\t\t\t\t见有人坠江，记者立即报警。但不到10秒，两人已被江水吞没。在事发现场的人行道上，遗留有两件黑夹克、一个女式提包、一瓶饮料和一个打火机。\n\t\t\t\t</dd></dl><br style=\"clear: both\" /><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/02/%e3%80%90%e5%9b%be%e8%af%b4%e5%a4%a9%e6%9c%9d%e3%80%91%e6%ad%a6%e6%b1%8910%e7%a7%92%e5%86%85%e4%b8%a4%e4%ba%ba%e8%b7%b3%e6%b1%9f/8ops8tuq00ap0001/'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/02/8OPS8TUQ00AP0001-150x150.jpg\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" aria-describedby=\"gallery-1-281341\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/02/8OPS8TUQ00AP0001-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/02/8OPS8TUQ00AP0001-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</dt>\n\t\t\t\t<dd class='wp-caption-text gallery-caption' id='gallery-1-281341'>\n\t\t\t\t2分钟后，民警赶到现场，并派快艇在落水区域搜寻。警方从遗留物品中找到一张名为刘某的身份证，显示该男子生于1993年5月，籍贯是黄陂区蔡店乡。\n\t\t\t\t</dd></dl><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon portrait'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/02/%e3%80%90%e5%9b%be%e8%af%b4%e5%a4%a9%e6%9c%9d%e3%80%91%e6%ad%a6%e6%b1%8910%e7%a7%92%e5%86%85%e4%b8%a4%e4%ba%ba%e8%b7%b3%e6%b1%9f/8ops8uoq00ap0001/'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/02/8OPS8UOQ00AP0001-150x150.jpg\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" aria-describedby=\"gallery-1-281342\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/02/8OPS8UOQ00AP0001-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/02/8OPS8UOQ00AP0001-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</dt>\n\t\t\t\t<dd class='wp-caption-text gallery-caption' id='gallery-1-281342'>\n\t\t\t\t武汉水上警方昨表示，民警一直打捞搜救到晚上6时。由于长江正处枯水季节，桥面距江面40多米，两人坠桥后生还希望渺茫，目前已通报下游沿江派出所，如发现踪迹，将及时进行身份比对。\n\t\t\t\t</dd></dl><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon portrait'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/02/%e3%80%90%e5%9b%be%e8%af%b4%e5%a4%a9%e6%9c%9d%e3%80%91%e6%ad%a6%e6%b1%8910%e7%a7%92%e5%86%85%e4%b8%a4%e4%ba%ba%e8%b7%b3%e6%b1%9f/8ops8vtj00ap0001/'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/02/8OPS8VTJ00AP0001-150x150.jpg\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" aria-describedby=\"gallery-1-281343\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/02/8OPS8VTJ00AP0001-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/02/8OPS8VTJ00AP0001-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</dt>\n\t\t\t\t<dd class='wp-caption-text gallery-caption' id='gallery-1-281343'>\n\t\t\t\t2月27日中午，武汉长江大桥武昌桥头堡，记者在此拍摄雾霾天气照片时，意外拍下轻生者跳桥。\n\t\t\t\t</dd></dl>\n\t\t\t<br style='clear: both' />\n\t\t</div>\n\n","author":1015,"categories":[18270,18269,10466,21627,13770],"tags":[13381,11955,22399]}